<span id=missiletrainer-inittrackingfrequency-trackingfrequency></span><h3 id='missiletrainer-inittrackingfrequency-trackingfrequency-'>MISSILETRAINER:InitTrackingFrequency(TrackingFrequency)</h3>
<p>Increases, decreases the missile tracking message display frequency with the provided time interval in seconds.
The default frequency is a 3 second interval, so the Tracking Frequency parameter specifies the increase or decrease from the default 3 seconds or the last frequency update.</p>

<h4> Parameters </h4>

<ul>
<li><a href="#missiletrainer-class-">MISSILETRAINER</a>
self</li>
<li><u>Number</u> TrackingFrequency : Provide a negative or positive value in seconds to incraese or decrease the display frequency.</li>
</ul>

<h4> Returns </h4>

<ul>
<li><a href="#missiletrainer-class-">MISSILETRAINER</a></li>
</ul>
