<span id=missiletrainer-oneventshot-eventdata></span><h3 id='missiletrainer-oneventshot-eventdata-'>MISSILETRAINER:OnEventShot(EventData)</h3>
<p>Detects if an SA site was shot with an anti radiation missile. In this case, take evasive actions based on the skill level set within the ME.</p>

<h4> Parameters </h4>

<ul>
<li><a href="#missiletrainer-class-">MISSILETRAINER</a>
self</li>
<li><a href="#eventdata-class-">EVENTDATA</a> EventData</li>
</ul>

<h4> Returns </h4>
